sequenceDiagram
    participant ScannerApp
    participant API
    participant TicketSvc
    participant DB as MongoDB

    ScannerApp->>API: POST /tickets/validate (qrSecret, scannerId)
    API->>TicketSvc: Verify QR secret
    TicketSvc->>DB: Query ticket by qrSecret
    DB-->>TicketSvc: Ticket details
    TicketSvc->>DB: Update check-in status
    TicketSvc-->>API: {status: VALID}
    API-->>ScannerApp: Display "VALID" (Green)
